[[File:Gear.png|thumb|600px|right|Aspects on equipment]]

Aspects are modifications to ship equipment that can add special benefits to the item the are modifying, or to the entire ship.

== '''Aspects''' ==

Aspects can fill the slot(s) underneath module items, and add special benefits like enhanced defense, critical chance, repair rates, added resistances etc.

Depending on rarity of the item one can find different number of aspects, or none at all. Some Aspects can fit onto all gear, others can be applied to specific modules, and some only on a single one.

Aspects can be removed in the [[Workshop]], which will destroy the item, but an extracted aspect can be applied onto another piece of equipment later.

=== '''Generation chance''' ===

When items are randomly generated, chance for item slots is determined by their rarity.
{| class="fandom-table"
|-
|Normal||None||
|-
|<span style="color:green">Enhanced</span>||Aspect 0-1||''25% chance of 1, 75% chance of 0''
|-
|<span style="color:Blue ">High Grade</span>||Aspect 1||''25% chance of 1 Rare, 75% chance of 1 Common''
|-
|<span style="color:purple">Exotic</span>||Aspect 1-2||''25% chance of 2 items (1 Rare + 1 Common), 75% chance of 1 item (1 Rare)''
|-
|<span style="color:orange">Legendary</span>||Aspect 2||''25% chance of 2 Rare, 75% chance of 2 items (1 Rare + 1 Common)''
|}

== Legend ==


;Rarity
: <span style="color:green">Common</span> &mdash; baseline aspect, drops on Enhanced+ items.
: <span style="color:purple">Rare</span> &mdash; rarer roll, drops on Exotic+ items.
;Slot
: Weapons &mdash; turret hardpoints.
: Dronebay &mdash; drone-bay modules.
: Hull / Armor &mdash; the named module type.
: Scanner &mdash; the scanner module.
: All Modules &mdash; any non-weapon module slot.
: All Items &mdash; any equipment slot.


